This paper is about benchmarking data warehouses, which is a topic related to database systems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DB (Database Systems and Applications). Other likely sub-categories include cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
